{"id":246,"parent_id":245,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":246,"title":"1 Samuel 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1","content":[["div",[".title","The First Book of",["br"],["span.dominant","Samuel"]],[".subtitle","Otherwise Called",["br"],"the First Book of the Kings"],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Hannah prays for a son and vows to give him to the Lord—Eli the priest blesses her—Samuel is born—Hannah loans him to the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.1","order":"02.10.001.20595"},["b","1"],"Now there was a certain man of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Ramathaim-zophim"],", of mount Ephraim, and his name",["i","was"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Elkanah"],", the son of Jeroham, the son of Elihu, the son of Tohu, the son of Zuph, an Ephrathite:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.2","order":"02.10.001.20596"},["b","2"],"And he had two wives; the name of the one",["i","was"],"Hannah, and the name of the other Peninnah: and Peninnah had children, but Hannah had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"no children"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.3","order":"02.10.001.20597"},["b","3"],"And this man went up out of his city",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"yearly"],"to worship and to sacrifice unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Shiloh"],". And the two sons of Eli, Hophni and Phinehas, the priests of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","were"],"there."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.4","order":"02.10.001.20598"},["b","4"],"¶And when the time was that Elkanah offered, he gave to Peninnah his wife, and to all her sons and her daughters, portions:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.5","order":"02.10.001.20599"},["b","5"],"But unto Hannah he gave a worthy portion; for he loved Hannah: but the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had shut up her womb."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.6","order":"02.10.001.20600"},["b","6"],"And her adversary also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"provoked"],"her sore, for to make her fret, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had shut up her womb."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.7","order":"02.10.001.20601"},["b","7"],"And",["i","as"],"he did so year by year, when she went up to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"house"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", so she provoked her; therefore she wept, and did not eat."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.8","order":"02.10.001.20602"},["b","8"],"Then said Elkanah her husband to her, Hannah, why weepest thou? and why eatest thou not? and why is thy heart grieved?",["i","am"],"not I better to thee than ten sons?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.9","order":"02.10.001.20603"},["b","9"],"¶So Hannah rose up after they had eaten in Shiloh, and after they had drunk. Now Eli the priest sat upon a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"seat"],"by a post of the temple of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.10","order":"02.10.001.20604"},["b","10"],"And she",["i","was"],"in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"bitterness"],"of soul, and prayed unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and wept sore."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.11","order":"02.10.001.20605"},["b","11"],"And she",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"vowed"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"vow"],", and said, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, if thou wilt indeed look on the affliction of thine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"handmaid"],", and remember me, and not forget thine handmaid, but wilt give unto thine handmaid a man child, then I will give him unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"all the days of his life, and there shall no",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"razor"],"come upon his head."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.12","order":"02.10.001.20606"},["b","12"],"And it came to pass, as she continued praying before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that Eli",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"marked"],"her mouth."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.13","order":"02.10.001.20607"},["b","13"],"Now Hannah, she spake in her heart; only her lips moved, but her voice was not heard: therefore Eli thought she had been drunken."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.14","order":"02.10.001.20608"},["b","14"],"And Eli said unto her, How long wilt thou be drunken? put away thy wine from thee."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.15","order":"02.10.001.20609"},["b","15"],"And Hannah answered and said, No, my lord, I",["i","am"],"a woman of a sorrowful spirit: I have drunk neither wine nor strong drink, but have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"poured"],"out my soul before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.16","order":"02.10.001.20610"},["b","16"],"Count not thine handmaid for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"daughter"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Belial"],": for out of the abundance of my complaint and grief have I spoken hitherto."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.17","order":"02.10.001.20611"},["b","17"],"Then Eli answered and said, Go in peace: and the God of Israel grant",["i","thee"],"thy petition that thou hast asked of him."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.18","order":"02.10.001.20612"},["b","18"],"And she said, Let thine handmaid find grace in thy sight. So the woman went her way, and did eat, and her countenance was no more",["i","sad."]],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.19","order":"02.10.001.20613"},["b","19"],"¶And they rose up in the morning early, and worshipped before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and returned, and came to their house to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Ramah"],": and Elkanah knew Hannah his wife; and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"remembered"],"her."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.20","order":"02.10.001.20614"},["b","20"],"Wherefore it came to pass, when the time was come about after Hannah had conceived, that she bare a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"son"],", and called his name Samuel,",["i","saying,"],"Because I have asked him of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.21","order":"02.10.001.20615"},["b","21"],"And the man Elkanah, and all his house, went up to offer unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"yearly"],"sacrifice, and his vow."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.22","order":"02.10.001.20616"},["b","22"],"But Hannah went not up; for she said unto her husband,",["i","I will not go up"],"until the child be weaned, and",["i","then"],"I will bring him, that he may appear before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and there abide for ever."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.23","order":"02.10.001.20617"},["b","23"],"And Elkanah her husband said unto her, Do what seemeth thee good; tarry until thou have weaned him; only the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"establish his word. So the woman abode, and gave her son suck until she weaned him."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.24","order":"02.10.001.20618"},["b","24"],"¶And when she had weaned him, she took him up with her, with three bullocks, and one ephah of flour, and a bottle of wine, and brought him unto the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in Shiloh: and the child",["i","was"],"young."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.25","order":"02.10.001.20619"},["b","25"],"And they slew a bullock, and brought the child to Eli."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.26","order":"02.10.001.20620"},["b","26"],"And she said, Oh my lord,",["i","as"],"thy soul liveth, my lord, I",["i","am"],"the woman that stood by thee here, praying unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.27","order":"02.10.001.20621"},["b","27"],"For this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"child"],"I prayed; and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath given me my petition which I asked of him:"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.28","order":"02.10.001.20622"},["b","28"],"Therefore also I have lent him to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; as long as he liveth he shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"lent"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". And he worshipped the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"there."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.1a","order":"02.10.001.20623"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.19"},"1 Sam. 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.1b","order":"02.10.001.20625"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/6.23.16-28"},"1 Chr. 6:23 (16–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.2a","order":"02.10.001.20627"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/barren"},"TG Barren"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.3a","order":"02.10.001.20629"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.21"},"1 Sam. 1:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.3b","order":"02.10.001.20631"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.1"},"Josh. 18:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.12"},"Jer. 7:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.6a","order":"02.10.001.20633"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.5.4-16"},"Gen. 16:5 (4–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/30.1"},"30:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.7a","order":"02.10.001.20635"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.9a","order":"02.10.001.20637"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/4.18"},"1 Sam. 4:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.10a","order":"02.10.001.20639"},["b","10a"],["span.small","OR"],"sadness, grief."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.11a","order":"02.10.001.20641"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/11.30.30-31"},"Judg. 11:30 (30–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.11b","order":"02.10.001.20643"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vow"},"TG Vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.11c","order":"02.10.001.20645"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.48.48-49"},"Luke 1:48 (48–49)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.11d","order":"02.10.001.20647"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.5.1-8"},"Num. 6:5 (1–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/13.5"},"Judg. 13:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.12a","order":"02.10.001.20649"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"saw."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.15a","order":"02.10.001.20651"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/enos/1.9"},"Enos 1:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.26.26-27"},"Alma 34:26 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.16a","order":"02.10.001.20653"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/13.13"},"Deut. 13:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.16b","order":"02.10.001.20655"},["b","16b"],["span.small","HEB"],"worthlessness; good-for-nothing, base wickedness.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.12"},"1 Sam. 2:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.19a","order":"02.10.001.20657"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.1"},"1 Sam. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.19b","order":"02.10.001.20659"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/30.22.22-23"},"Gen. 30:22 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.20a","order":"02.10.001.20661"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-motherhood"},"TG Marriage, Motherhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.21a","order":"02.10.001.20663"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.3"},"1 Sam. 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.27a","order":"02.10.001.20665"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-motherhood"},"TG Marriage, Motherhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.28a","order":"02.10.001.20667"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.20"},"1 Sam. 2:20"],"."]]}
